data.description: SANDY BEACH in MERIFIELD ACRES with a deep water DOCK enjoying sunset views. This 3 Bedroom/2 Bath Home offers a FULL BASEMENT for your expansion- the NEW Heat Pump and flooring done & stubbed for a full bath - French Doors open to your covered Patio lakeside .The main level features Hardwood Floors with both formal & informal areas. You will enjoy relaxing on the Lakeside Sun Room & Screened Porch. This Fall the wrap Porch will be the place to rock away! The Kitchen has room for a Breakfast nook (hard tile, Pantry Cabinet & Granite Counters). Flight enthusiasts will appreciate being right near the Air Strip. So many different places to relax- perfect for having guests come & stay !Other amenities of Merifield Acres include miles of roads to walk, bike or jog, Tennis (used for Pickle Ball too),high speed internet with SHENTEL .Minutes to golf at Kinderton Country Club & the small Town charm of Clarksville On The Lake. Enjoy your Kerr Lake Dream right here!
